title: Skyrim - Steam paid mod SkyUI 5
description:
So, just when you thought the shitstorm of idiocy is over, the author of SkyUI, the must-have mod for Skyrim has cowardly hid behind the paywall, and announced that the 5th update is going to be paid. 

Oh, if only we could get it somehow. 

Includes: modified SKSE + SKYUI 5, with no working map (crashes). Map fix works, thought it shows up an error code. 

I have no idea if that works with your favourite anime titties mod
